\caption{Provenance where the seeds were sourced from are depicted as circles, while the diamond denotes the location of the common garden. The common garden location is where the study took place at the Weld Research Building (Boston, MA). The colors of the dots match the model estimates of Figure \ref{fig:wcmuplotasite}.}
\label{fig:mapProv}
