\Sexpr{aspp_df2$p95[which(aspp_df2$spp_name == "B. papyrifera")]} RW; {\Bpop}: $\alpha =$
\Sexpr{aspp_df2$mean[which(aspp_df2$spp_name == "B. populifolia")]}, UI:
\Sexpr{aspp_df2$p5[which(aspp_df2$spp_name == "B. populifolia")]}, 
\Sexpr{aspp_df2$p95[which(aspp_df2$spp_name == "B. populifolia")]} RW; Figure \ref{fig:wcxyGDD} and \ref{fig:wcxyGSL}; Table \ref{tab:tab_all}). In addition, growth did not vary with provenance (Dartmouth College (NH): $\alpha =$
